780static inline JSC::EncodedJSValue jsDOMMatrixReadOnlyConstructorFunction_fromMatrixBody(JSC::JSGlobalObject* lexicalGlobalObject, JSC::CallFrame* callFrame)
781{
782 auto& vm = JSC::getVM(lexicalGlobalObject);
783 auto throwScope = DECLARE_THROW_SCOPE(vm);
784 UNUSED_PARAM(throwScope);
785 UNUSED_PARAM(callFrame);
786 EnsureStillAliveScope argument0 = callFrame->argument(0);
787 auto other = convert<IDLDictionary<DOMMatrixInit>>(*lexicalGlobalObject, argument0.value());
788 RETURN_IF_EXCEPTION(throwScope, encodedJSValue());
789 RELEASE_AND_RETURN(throwScope, JSValue::encode(toJSNewlyCreated<IDLInterface<DOMMatrixReadOnly>>(*lexicalGlobalObject, *jsCast<JSDOMGlobalObject*>(lexicalGlobalObject), throwScope, DOMMatrixReadOnly::fromMatrix(WTFMove(other)))));
790}

797static inline JSC::EncodedJSValue jsDOMMatrixReadOnlyConstructorFunction_fromFloat32ArrayBody(JSC::JSGlobalObject* lexicalGlobalObject, JSC::CallFrame* callFrame)
798{
799 auto& vm = JSC::getVM(lexicalGlobalObject);
800 auto throwScope = DECLARE_THROW_SCOPE(vm);
801 UNUSED_PARAM(throwScope);
802 UNUSED_PARAM(callFrame);
803 if (UNLIKELY(callFrame->argumentCount() < 1))
804 return throwVMError(lexicalGlobalObject, throwScope, createNotEnoughArgumentsError(lexicalGlobalObject));
805 EnsureStillAliveScope argument0 = callFrame->uncheckedArgument(0);
806 auto array32 = convert<IDLFloat32Array>(*lexicalGlobalObject, argument0.value(), [](JSC::JSGlobalObject& lexicalGlobalObject, JSC::ThrowScope& scope) { throwArgumentTypeError(lexicalGlobalObject, scope, 0, "array32", "DOMMatrixReadOnly", "fromFloat32Array", "Float32Array"); });
807 RETURN_IF_EXCEPTION(throwScope, encodedJSValue());
808 RELEASE_AND_RETURN(throwScope, JSValue::encode(toJSNewlyCreated<IDLInterface<DOMMatrixReadOnly>>(*lexicalGlobalObject, *jsCast<JSDOMGlobalObject*>(lexicalGlobalObject), throwScope, DOMMatrixReadOnly::fromFloat32Array(array32.releaseNonNull()))));
809}

1240JSC::IsoSubspace* JSDOMMatrixReadOnly::subspaceForImpl(JSC::VM& vm)
1241{
1242 auto& clientData = *static_cast<JSVMClientData*>(vm.clientData);
1243 auto& spaces = clientData.subspaces();
1244 if (auto* space = spaces.m_subspaceForDOMMatrixReadOnly.get())
1245 return space;
1246 static_assert(std::is_base_of_v<JSC::JSDestructibleObject, JSDOMMatrixReadOnly> || !JSDOMMatrixReadOnly::needsDestruction);
1247 if constexpr (std::is_base_of_v<JSC::JSDestructibleObject, JSDOMMatrixReadOnly>)
1248 spaces.m_subspaceForDOMMatrixReadOnly = makeUnique<IsoSubspace> ISO_SUBSPACE_INIT(vm.heap, vm.destructibleObjectHeapCellType.get(), JSDOMMatrixReadOnly);
1249 else
1250 spaces.m_subspaceForDOMMatrixReadOnly = makeUnique<IsoSubspace> ISO_SUBSPACE_INIT(vm.heap, vm.cellHeapCellType.get(), JSDOMMatrixReadOnly);
1251 auto* space = spaces.m_subspaceForDOMMatrixReadOnly.get();
1252IGNORE_WARNINGS_BEGIN("unreachable-code")
1253IGNORE_WARNINGS_BEGIN("tautological-compare")
1254 void (*myVisitOutputConstraint)(JSC::JSCell*, JSC::SlotVisitor&) = JSDOMMatrixReadOnly::visitOutputConstraints;
1255 void (*jsCellVisitOutputConstraint)(JSC::JSCell*, JSC::SlotVisitor&) = JSC::JSCell::visitOutputConstraints;
1256 if (myVisitOutputConstraint != jsCellVisitOutputConstraint)
1257 clientData.outputConstraintSpaces().append(space);
1258IGNORE_WARNINGS_END
1259IGNORE_WARNINGS_END
1260 return space;
1261}
